comments: Grant (DEN) makes marginal contact with Mitchell (UTA) on the perimeter.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) is already in O'Neale's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Gobert (UTA) is already in Grant's (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Murray (DEN) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Grant (DEN) is already in Gobert's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Gobert (UTA) moves laterally into Jokic's (DEN) path and affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs prior to Jokic's gather.
Millsap (DEN) legally moves alongside of Mitchell (UTA) on his path to the basket and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) is already in Grant's (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Grant (DEN) trips Mitchell (UTA) and affects his SQBR.
O'Neale (UTA) is moving alongside Murray's (DEN) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Murray on the perimeter.
Ingles (UTA) briefly grasps Jokic's (DEN) jersey and immediately releases it.
Gobert (UTA) does not maintain verticality and brings his arm down, making contact with Murray's (DEN) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Morris (DEN) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Ingles (UTA) makes marginal contact with Murray (DEN) as he attempts to establish himself in a guarding position in his path on the perimeter.
Murray (DEN) braces himself for the contact with Ingles (UTA) with his off-arm and releases without extending into Ingles.
Mitchell (UTA) extends his arms into Grant's (DEN) body and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Grant (DEN) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) trips Murray (DEN) during his drive and affects his SQBR.
Porter Jr. (DEN) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
